channel.title: RuneScape 317 Remake (REBORN!)
channel.description:
[center]RuneRemake Base: Shards
[b]Summary[/b]
This development team will be bringing back RuneScape in 2006-2007. To bring back the feeling you got when you pked full rune or even an abyssal whip. You may thing "Oh just another failed remake" but I myself will not stop until I have perfected this server. I'm not working on only combat and pking but skills also. I plan to perfect every skill. Combat will be a big part also. I have come to realize that it would really take a while to do this on my own so that's where this development team comes in. [/center] [b][center]Proof i'm using shards.[/center][/b][center][IMG]http://i356.photobucket.com/albums/oo5/xloggernubs/IronScape-1.jpg[/img][/center]
Developers Server:[Pkpoison][OPEN] Client:[OPEN][OPEN] Web designers[OPEN][OPEN] Gfx: [OPEN][OPEN]
[b][i]Only apply if you are as dedicated as I am. This isn't a 4 day development it's going to take a while.[/i][/b] [code] Applications Age: Timezone: Period of time on a day: Days a week online: Position: experience: msn: [/code]
Goals: All skills 100% All of RuneScape sounds RuneScape songs in most areas. Lots more.
